OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FBritain will replace its current
OL,7,Fageing destroyers with six smaller
OL,8,F"hybrid" warships as it focuses on
OL,9,Fmodernising the military under changes
OL,10,Fto the long-awaited defence investment
OL,11,Fplan (Dip).
OL,13,FThe Royal Navy will procure at least
OL,14,Fsix so-called "common combat vessels"
OL,15,F(CCVs), which will act as command hubs
OL,16,Ffor uncrewed systems, with delivery
OL,17,Fexpected in the 2030s, the Ministry of
OL,18,FDefence said on Monday.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FThe new vessels are part of efforts to
OL,7,Fexpand the Navy's reach and firepower
OL,8,Fwithout a "proportional increase" in
OL,9,Fcrew or cost, and will work alongside
OL,10,Feight Type 26 and five Type 31 crewed
OL,11,Ffrigates - a type of warship.
OL,13,FUnderwater drones and sensor platforms
OL,14,Fwill also feature heavily after
OL,15,Fministers warned of rising Russian
OL,16,Fsubmarine activity in the Atlantic
OL,17,Fnear critical undersea cables.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
