PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer is
OL,7,Fexpected to unveil the blueprint for
OL,8,Ffuture-proofing the UK's armed forces
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, as a potential legacy
OL,10,Fproject before he leaves No 10, which
OL,11,Fcould be as soon as July 20.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
