OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FEarlier proposals to replace the
OL,7,FNavy's fleet of six Type 45 destroyers
OL,8,Fwith a new class of guided-missile
OL,9,Fwarship, the Type 83 destroyer, will
OL,10,Fno longer appear in the Dip.
OL,12,FThe Dip was initially due to be
OL,13,Fpublished last year, but has been
OL,14,Fdelayed after rows over the amount of
OL,15,Fmoney promised, which prompted John
OL,16,FHealey to quit as defence secretary in
OL,17,Fprotest earlier this month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FHis successor Dan Jarvis is understood
OL,7,Fto have secured some extra money for
OL,8,Fthe plan, taking the settlement to
OL,9,Faround #14.5 billion ` up from the
OL,10,F#13.5 billion offered to Healey, but
OL,11,Fstill short of the #28 billion
OL,12,Fofficials previously said was needed.
OL,14,F"Our Royal Navy is a formidable force,
OL,15,Foperating to protect our nation and
OL,16,Four allies in the Atlantic and
OL,17,Fbeyond," Jarvis said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,F"These common combat vessels will
OL,7,Fprovide our dedicated sailors with
OL,8,Fhybrid ships that are designed and
OL,9,Fbuilt for the increasing threats we
OL,10,Fface.
OL,12,F"Developed with exceptional British
OL,13,Finnovators, the new ships will be
OL,14,FBritish-built, supporting jobs across
OL,15,Fthe nation and giving the Royal Navy a
OL,16,Fcapability built for modern warfare."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FThe plans come as First Sea Admiral
OL,7,FGeneral Sir Gwyn Jenkins leads efforts
OL,8,Fto shift towards a new "hybrid Navy",
OL,9,Fmade up of both traditional crewed
OL,10,Fships, submarines, autonomous vehicles
OL,11,Fand AI.
OL,13,FThe programme will also "anchor" three
OL,14,Fnew Atlantic programmes ` Atlantic
OL,15,FBastion, Atlantic Shield and Atlantic
OL,16,FStrike ` designed to counter Russian
OL,17,Factivity in the North Atlantic and
OL,18,FHigh North, officials said.
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@YOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FElsewhere, #500 million will be
OL,7,Fpromised to Britain's commandos under
OL,8,Fchanges to the Dip drawn up by Jarvis
OL,9,Fas he seeks to put his stamp on the
OL,10,Flong-awaited blueprint.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for No10 said that the
OL,13,Fpriority was to get the latest kit
OL,14,Finto the hands of military personnel,
OL,15,Fwith the funding to be put towards
OL,16,Fhigh speed boats and drone and
OL,17,Fautonomous technology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FIt will partly also go towards new
OL,7,Fhigh-speed commando insertion craft `
OL,8,Fspecial vessels used to covertly
OL,9,Ftransport troops from the rapid-
OL,10,Fresponse force ` which officials said
OL,11,Fcould be used for operations including
OL,12,Fthe seizure of Russian shadow fleet
OL,13,Fvessels.
OL,15,FStarmer will press ahead with
OL,16,Fpublishing the Dip before he resigns
OL,17,Fas PM, with Andy Burnham tipped to be
OL,18,Fhis successor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FBut the former Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fmayor, who has been authorised to
OL,8,Freceive government briefings from the
OL,9,Fcivil service as he prepares for
OL,10,Fpower, has also seen and signed off on
OL,11,Fthe blueprint, the Sunday Times
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FOpposition critics have described the
OL,15,Fsuggested #1 billion uplift as a "drop
OL,16,Fin the ocean", while a former chief of
OL,17,Fdefence staff said Burnham may need to
OL,18,Ffind more money once he reaches office.
OL,26,@wD@bOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FAdmiral Sir Tony Radakin told the BBC
OL,7,Fthat the next leader would need to
OL,8,Foperate "almost like a wartime prime
OL,9,Fminister" in light of global conflicts
OL,10,Fin countries like Ukraine, Iran and
OL,11,FLebanon.
OL,13,FResponding to Burnham calling his
OL,14,Felection the "Makerfield test", Sir
OL,15,FTonysaid: "I would say it's the Moscow
OL,16,Ftest."
OL,18,FShadow defence secretary James
OL,19,FCartlidge said the plans were "too
OL,20,Flittle, too late".
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@IO]wD@KOUxD@FO]{D@_OU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,F"If correct, these reports suggest
OL,7,FLabour's long-delayed defence plan
OL,8,Fwill have barely any more cash than
OL,9,Fthe previous one ` which their own
OL,10,Fformer Defence Secretary John Healey
OL,11,Fsaid in his resignation letter would
OL,12,Fmake Britain 'less safe'," he said.
OL,14,F"How can that situation have changed
OL,15,Fwith such a small addition of cash?
OL,17,F"So it's no surprise we are hearing
OL,18,Freports of capabilities being
OL,19,Fscrapped, just at the time we are
OL,20,Fmeant to be strengthening our armed
OL,21,Fforces."
OL,26,@nD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782755283
OL,3,CUK's ageing destroyers to be replaced
OL,4,Cwith drone hubs under new defence plan
OL,6,FHe added: "This is no way to run a
OL,7,Fcountry and the brilliant men and
OL,8,Fwomen of our armed forces deserve much
OL,9,Fbetter."
OL,11,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,12,Four political experts are across all
OL,13,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,14,Fto the latest episode below...
